Class GetURL2

java.lang.Object
  com.jswiff.swfrecords.actions.Action
      com.jswiff.swfrecords.actions.GetURL2
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class GetURL2
extends Action

Gets contents from an URL or exchanges data with a server.

Performed stack operations:
pop target (see GetURL)
pop url

ActionScript equivalent: getURL(), loadMovie(), loadMovieNum(), loadVariables()

Since:
SWF 4
See Also:
GetURL, Serialized Form

Constructor Detail

GetURL2

public GetURL2(byte sendVarsMethod,
               boolean loadTarget,
               boolean loadVariables)
Creates a new GetURL2 action.

Parameters:
sendVarsMethod - HTTP request method (METHOD_NONE, METHOD_GET or METHOD_POST)
loadTarget - false if target is a browser frame, true if it is a path to a clip (in slash syntax - /parentClip/childClip - or dot syntax - parentClip.childClip)
loadVariables - if true, the server is expected to respond with an url encoded set of variables
